</div>
<div>
<p>武德<measure quantity="6" unit="years">
<num value="6">六</num>年</measure>反<pc>，</pc>輔公祏以為西南道大行臺<pc>。</pc>善安掠孫州<pc>，</pc>執<term>總管</term>王戎<pc>，</pc>襲殺<placeName>黃州</placeName>
<term>總管</term>
<persName>周法明</persName>
<pc>。</pc>會<persName>李大亮</persName>兵至<pc>，</pc>為開曉禍福<pc>，</pc>答曰<pc>：</pc>
